--></style><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />
呼籲政府基於人道考量，讓陳前總統保外就醫</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 9pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本黨長期關心陳前總統健康狀況與醫療人權，日前據多位專業醫師診斷，今陳前總統所患疾病甚多，健康狀況嚴重惡化，卻未能獲得適當的醫療照護，其所受之不人道待遇，為舉世成熟民主國家前所未見。有鑑陳前總統係卸任國家元首，倘在獄中有任何意外，勢將引發社會極大爭議與對立，邇來，屢有意見領袖及媒體社論出面呼籲政府應儘速讓陳前總統保外就醫，實乃超越黨派、藍綠之儻見，更逐漸成為社會各界之共識。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:9.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.5gd;
text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:
exactly"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 為促進政治和諧，降低社會對立，本黨在陳菊市長代理主席期間，曾兩度通過決議，呼籲政府基於人道考量，讓陳前總統保外就醫。為達此一目的，本人於就職黨主席後，即在<span lang="EN-US">6</span>月<span lang="EN-US">27</span>日中執會再度決議，為避免社會付出無謂代價，本黨將協調各級民代，透過各級民意機關聲援陳前總統醫療人權，並聯繫各界意見領袖發揮影響力，透過社會集體的力量，俾早日解決此一問題。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:9.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.5gd;
text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:
exactly"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 日前，本黨已發函促請各縣市黨籍議員，透過本黨議會黨團在各縣市議會提案，呼籲政府體察民情，讓陳前總統儘速保外就醫；近日台大醫院柯文哲醫師與多名重量級醫界人士正在推動連署，呼籲政府儘速讓陳前總統保外就醫，本人亦已於日前連署，在此，希冀 閣下以醫療人權為本，以社會和諧為念，能夠發揮影響力，共同參與連署，為社會消弭爭議，為台灣化解對立，讓台灣更進一步。再度感謝，並祝</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:9.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.5gd;
text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:
exactly"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:標楷體">闔家安康</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:9.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.5gd;
text-indent:203.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:14.5;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:
exactly;tab-stops:304.5pt right 415.3pt"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:標楷體">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:9.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:.5gd;
text-indent:203.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:14.5;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:
exactly;tab-stops:304.5pt right 415.3pt"><span style="font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:標楷體">主席<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-tab-count:2">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: larger;">蘇貞昌</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:標楷體"><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-tab-count:2">&nbsp; </span></span>敬上</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p align="right" class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:9.0pt;mso-para-margin-bottom:
.5gd;text-align:right;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 9pt; text-align: left; line-height: 23pt;"><a href="http://campaign.tw-npo.org/sign.php?id=2012072222223600" target="_blank" id="" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><span style="font-size: larger;">http://campaign.tw-npo.org/</span><wbr></wbr><span style="font-size: larger;">sign.php?id=2012072222223600</span></a><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline ! important; float: none;"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br />
保外救醫連結</span></span></p>	                	            </div>
